{"tid":2276880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望光復香港製造業 港產港銷","createTime":"2020-11-08T05:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:40:09.000Z","uid":4672,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71d150c046859909c943a80233f90805b770b3f4","tid":2276880,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"今次疫情重新睇到大量「香港製造」 <br />\n令我有少少感觸 <br />\n香港人原來願意洗多少少錢購買香港本土產品<br />\n香港人經濟實力完全足夠滿足香港製造業<br />\n只係之前未有選擇 <br />\n依家 重新發展我地既製造業 唔一定要俾鄰國平<br />\n只要品質好 價錢公道 而且有「香港製造」信心底下<br />\n我相信港人願意買返自己產既商品<br />\n<br />\n如果我地自己都唔相信「香港製造」<br />\n外國人又點會相信？<br />\n<br />\n如果我地自己都唔選擇「香港製造」<br />\n外國人又點會選擇？"},{"pid":"364e2615da0544316b088440ec1aee9ca3bfd4a7","tid":2276880,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cad5cfb9d0ab012a3a156b2404cf3a072fc4819","tid":2276880,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"依家只有中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b5b83b457f9884b9c9a20f22ff0a6199379896","tid":2276880,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cad5cfb9d0ab012a3a156b2404cf3a072fc4819","tid":2276880,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"依家只有中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"全球災難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814ae5188212313bab822531bef1cbf47b07373e","tid":2276880,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:21:26.000Z","msg":"同樣貨品，香港製造要貴一倍仲買唔買？"},{"pid":"457cca646821c0e90088dbc87ec7c9f3fce707e5","tid":2276880,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e45114925edcdfd65edd5c22f80c51be